# sakura_cloudhsm_license (Data Source)

Get information about an existing CloudHSM License.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "sakura_cloudhsm_license" "foobar" {
  name = "foobar"
  # or
  # id = "cloudhsm-license-resource-id"
}
```

## Schema

### Optional

- `id` (String) The ID of the CloudHSM License.
- `name` (String) The name of the CloudHSM License.
- `tags` (Set of String) The tags of the CloudHSM License.
- `zone` (String) The zone of the CloudHSM License. This must be one of [`is1b`/`tk1a`]

### Read-Only

- `created_at` (String) The creation date of the CloudHSM License
- `description` (String) The description of the CloudHSM License.
- `modified_at` (String) The modification date of the CloudHSM License
